Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.64,0:01:47.58,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淑女与武士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.22,0:01:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜兰克·居尔布
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯特利亚国王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.29,0:01:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是提高声望的最佳舞台呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗杀国王么..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 只是个把观光当国家产业的小国
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且身为初出茅庐的暗杀者既能在业界中提高声望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那报酬也绝对少不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委托人是他的亲人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不用你管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我保证绝不会演变成外交问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.石川..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯特利亚大公国国家展览会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:26.67,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Principaute De astria Exposition Nationale
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可谓..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界的宝贝齐聚一堂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冰冰冰淇淋给给给你！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗斗斗斗牛犬在在那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布布布丁冻糕呀呀呀呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:03:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聚在一块朋友多多..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 发现武士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔科
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸喜欢的一张画呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 武士！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武~武武武..武士之友！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种歌词 妈妈写的曲子里没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚想出来的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武武武士之友..呀呀呀吼~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以妨碍到叔叔们的工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就回国了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们先回旅馆休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们一边唱朋朋朋友之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边比赛谁能最快跑回旅馆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备唱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冰冰冰淇淋给给给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冰冰冰淇淋给给给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗斗斗斗牛犬在在那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武武武武士之友呀呀呀吼！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔科
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发前进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想必也很累了吧 杜兰克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 外交可没那么轻松呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是能和孙子们一起共渡周末时光真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女教师也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是指玛利亚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是约聘到秋天的临时家教 但是做的确实不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 如果女儿能有她一半的能耐的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜兰克大人 这件事就不要再提了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐已经嫁到舒梅特家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 父王不可能听得进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇太子已经死了 因为交通事故..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 失去哥哥的父王终日陷于惆怅之中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来的王女是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我就是..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥留下的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔科才是继承人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还只是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么掌管得了这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是这个时候才是我们出场的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做全凭父王的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不打算照看那三个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 葛瑞丝你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:05:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巴黎的淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像妈妈一样..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛瑞丝 妈妈已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是..可是露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不是说好不哭的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冰冰冰淇淋给给给..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我拿冰淇淋来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔科 危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武..武武士之友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 马尔科很喜欢武士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前在卢浮宫博物馆也对浮世绘特别感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那几个小孩嘴里唱的武士之友到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是她们姐弟三人喜欢的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士之友是.. 我想就是同伴的意思吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友是同伴么..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你就是他们的母亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我只是一个普通的家教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那几个孩子的双亲三年前因事故去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫玛利亚 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下是..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用茶 武士之友！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫马尔科吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂男子汉不要因区区冰淇淋而轻易落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是男子汉的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 男子汉的约定！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到这里居然有武士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么之前都没有发现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 兔子先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满月之夜月兔现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日本的景物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下名为石川五卫门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一名流浪艺人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石川先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看呀看呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:08:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔科
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.76,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}继承人的血缘之争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.76,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}箭头指向舒梅特男爵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面把舒梅特讲成继承人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承人是马尔科大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜兰克大人 这文章看了有害无益
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在马尔科成人之前 我会保护这个国家！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有害无益么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实斩了个无谓之物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被女色所迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切舍御免！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:51.45,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}切舍御免：格杀勿论。是日本武士之特权，受到贱民无礼对待之时，可当场斩杀不守责罚。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来我这探险吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..刚才有个武士好帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少..此时留他们一刻安详才是武士之义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:09.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(615,610)}甜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 武士先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 在日本还有像你一样的武士..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非也 现在的日本根本没有武士的容身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才开始了旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在下是..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里都找不到自己的容身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你有那些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:10:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朋友在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我只是一个微不足道的临时约聘的家教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么晚安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士之友先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一般的杂耍艺人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发前进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜兰克国王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.石川..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停..停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧..紧急联络！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列车失控了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 无法取得联络
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜兰克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按这个速度下去 列车很快就会脱轨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底出了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 你们..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人搞破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员被人杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您应该很清楚是谁干的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个玩杂耍的竟如此出言不逊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回座位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有刺客！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把刀扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管 开枪吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士之友！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世间万物..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有此斩铁之剑切不断的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好..好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是何方圣神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下的名字是石川五卫门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:14:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下是前来取你的性命的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然冒充成杂耍艺人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞破坏的也是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个事态..并非在下所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来听听你要说什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托兰克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚老师 让孩子们和乘客赶紧去避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到列车的最后一节
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的错要归咎于在下的稚嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石川先生..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔科说要去救爸爸的画
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 你们俩先逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是暗杀么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因不相信在下的手段才出此下策..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一开始就是双重的计划吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人就是这样的小人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然在下也成了他们的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没必要取你性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个事态 请让我来负责吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔科去了货物车厢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的武士..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔科！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想把加速减到最小
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,货物车厢的重量实在太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是国宝都放在那个车厢里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国宝和小孩子的性命哪个更重要？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧 马尔科
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师..好帅..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔科！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我们赶紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:15:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 玛利亚老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士之友会救我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会哭的 因为和他约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好样的 马尔科
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚老师 请抓紧时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我要把孩子们固定好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家请拿一些皮带给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的..够不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚老师 用我的皮带
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又斩了无谓之物..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 全世界的宝贝统统都..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冰冰冰淇淋给给给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗斗斗斗牛犬在在那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武武武武士之友吼吼吼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聚在一块朋友多多~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福 我们得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟你道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无须道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下乃生活在暗处之人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请跟孩子们..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟马尔科道个别
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会和朋友相逢..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.49,0:17:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛瑞丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔科
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我们回城堡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都没事真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.石川
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男爵您应该心里明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请跟我们走一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒梅特男爵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士之友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔科 要成为了不起的国王哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你什么时候开始在这等的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是同类么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 武士之友先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是刺客..或是盗贼么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国宝也都付之一炬了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好白费功夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那些孩子得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托了你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太看得起我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是那块料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是何许人也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报上名来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何许人也？只是一个女人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊 是大公国代代传下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}传说中奥古斯特·罗丹偷偷送给情人卡米耶·克洛岱尔的..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“哀求的国王”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就是以这个为目标么..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 全部都是在演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？很受打击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这样就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..所以你也同为天涯沦落人呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况谁都没有真正的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和在下的话..可以做真正的..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和在下的话 可以做真正的什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是峰不二子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有缘再会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出色的武士之友先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做真正的女朋友..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会啦 五卫门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,峰..不二子酱..么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是何许人也！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又斩了无谓之物..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待续
